'''李·里格比謀殺案'''，又稱'''2013年伍利奇襲擊事件'''，發生於[[伍爾維奇|伍爾維奇]]當地時間2013年5月22日下午2時20分左右，[[英國陸軍|英國陸軍]][[皇家近衛團|皇家近衛團]][[軍樂隊|軍樂隊]][[鼓手|鼓手]]李·里格比（{{lang-en|Lee Rigby}}）下班後途經[[倫敦|倫敦]]東南[[伍利奇|伍利奇]]惠靈頓街時，被兩名襲擊者殺害<ref name="rigby" /><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Woolwich attack: Killed man 'was soldier'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22634468#TWEET765325|publisher=BBC News|date=23 May 2013|5=|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523170328/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22634468#TWEET765325|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name-"InsideGovernment">{{en}}{{cite web|title=Woolwich attack victim confirmed as serving soldier|publisher=Ministry of Defence, Prime Ministers Office, Home Office|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/woolwich-attack-victim-confirmed-as-serving-soldier|archive-date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002023304/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/woolwich-attack-victim-confirmed-as-serving-soldier|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

里格比先被車輛撞倒<ref name=guardian-man-killed-in-deadly-terror-attack-in-london-street>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Man killed in deadly terror attack in London street|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/22/police-respond-serious-incident-woolwich|work=The Guardian|last=Dodd|first=Vikram|date=22 May 2013|accessdate=22 May 2013|archive-date=2013-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709175137/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/22/police-respond-serious-incident-woolwich|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後被兩名襲擊者以[[刀|刀]]及[[菜刀|菜刀]]斬死<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10074881/Mum-talked-down-Woolwich-terrorists-who-told-her-We-want-to-start-a-war-in-London-tonight.html|title=Mum talked down Woolwich terrorists who told her: 'We want to start a war in London tonight'|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523010507/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10074881/Mum-talked-down-Woolwich-terrorists-who-told-her-We-want-to-start-a-war-in-London-tonight.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後他們將屍體拖出馬路，待在原地直至警察到來。襲擊者向路人宣示，因為英國軍隊殺害[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]所以才殺死士兵報復。他們被警察射擊倒地，分別送往不同的醫院，病況嚴重<ref name='BBC'>{{en}}{{cite web|title=Woolwich machete attack leaves man dead|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22630303|publisher=BBC News|date=22 May 2013|accessdate=22 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522182215/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22630303|dead-url=no}}</ref>。襲擊者都是[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]裔英國[[英國穆斯林|穆斯林]]<ref name=Suspects/>。他們是[[獨狼恐怖分子|獨狼恐怖分子]]，不隸屬任何[[恐怖組織|恐怖組織]]。

英國政治和宗教領袖，包括[[倫敦的穆斯林|倫敦伊斯蘭社區]]譴責這次恐怖襲擊<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=UK Muslim groups condemn London slaying, urge leaders to act|first=Laura|last=Smith-Spark|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/23/world/europe/uk-attack-muslims|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=24 May 2013|accessdate=24 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610061953/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/05/23/world/europe/uk-attack-muslims|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/05/22/woolwich-death-reaction-to-machete-terror-attack-3805361/|title=Woolwich attack: Religious groups and Boris Johnson condemn brutal killing|date=22 May 2013|newspaper=Metro|author=Richard James|accessdate=25 May 2013|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129020458/https://metro.co.uk/2013/05/22/woolwich-death-reaction-to-machete-terror-attack-3805361/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，世界各國也相繼譴責襲擊<ref name=BBC20130524>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22653147|title=World press condemns Woolwich killing|date=24 May 2013|newspaper=BBC|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-date=2013-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609131926/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22653147|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==受害者==

[[File:Drummer_Lee_Rigby_1.jpg|thumb]]

被殺的士兵李·里格比，是25歲的英國陸軍皇家近衛團第二營軍樂隊鼓手，來自[[大曼徹斯特|大曼徹斯特]][[米德爾頓|米德爾頓]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Woolwich soldier murder victim named as Lee Rigby from Middleton|first=Dan|last=Thompson|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/woolwich-soldier-murder-victim-named-4007798|newspaper=[[Manchester_Evening_News|Manchester Evening News]]|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729134509/http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/greater-manchester-news/woolwich-soldier-murder-victim-named-4007798|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於[[倫敦塔|倫敦塔]]當招聘人員和助理，曾經在[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]、[[德國|德國]]和[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]服役。里格比有前妻和兩歲的兒子<ref name="rigby">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22644857|title=Woolwich attack: Lee Rigby named as victim|publisher=BBC News|date=23 May 2013|location=London|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911210643/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22644857|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==襲擊==

英國警方於下午2時20分收到一宗關於惠靈頓街發生襲擊事件的求救電話，惠靈頓街接近伍爾維奇[[南部循環路|南部循環路]]一部約翰·威爾遜街交界，離里格比駐守的[[皇家砲兵營|皇家砲兵營]]有300至400米遠<ref name=guardian-man-killed-in-deadly-terror-attack-in-london-street/>。李·里格比當時下班，據報身穿印有「[[英雄救援|英雄救援]]」字樣的T恤<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/machete-attack-soldier-woolwich-london |title=Serving soldier killed in Woolwich street attack – Channel 4 News |publisher=Channel 4 |access-date=2013-05-24 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005637/http://www.channel4.com/news/machete-attack-soldier-woolwich-london |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相信他被一輛沃克斯豪爾車蓄意撞倒<ref name="guard3">{{en}}{{cite web|author=Sandra Laville, Shiv Malik and Ben Quinn|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/22/woolwich-attack-horror-soldier|title=Woolwich killing: horror on John Wilson Street|work=The Guardian|date=22 May 2013|accessdate=22 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623204105/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/22/woolwich-attack-horror-soldier|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並被兩名襲擊者用[[刀|刀]]和[[菜刀|菜刀]]亂刀斬死，而且襲擊者嘗試將屍體斬首<ref name='BBC'/><ref name=guardian-man-killed-in-deadly-terror-attack-in-london-street/><ref name=Telegraph24>{{en}}''The Daily Telegraph'' [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10073910/Woolwich-attack-terrorist-proclaimed-an-eye-for-an-eye-after-attack.html Woolwich attack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10073910/Woolwich-attack-terrorist-proclaimed-an-eye-for-an-eye-after-attack.html |date=20130523164434 }}, 24 May 2013, (retrieved 24 May 2013)</ref>。據稱其中一名襲擊者在襲擊後高呼「[[大讚辭|真主至大]]」<ref name="washingtontimes1">{{en}}{{cite news|title=London terror suspects shout 'Allahu Akbar' and machete man to death|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2013/may/22/london-terror-suspects-shout-allahu-akbar-and-mach/|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204152435/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2013/may/22/london-terror-suspects-shout-allahu-akbar-and-mach/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

襲擊後迅間，兩名女士趕到里格比身邊，嘗試保護他免被進一步的襲擊<ref name="guard3"/>。英格麗·洛約-肯奈特是其中一名目擊者，她當時是短程巴士的搭客，以為面前發生的是普通車禍，立即下車意圖為里格比進行急救，她發現里格比已死，而且顯然死於謀殺，於是向襲擊者展開談話，問他想怎樣。一名襲擊者據聞如此回話：「今晚我們想在倫敦發動戰爭。」她回答：「你輸定了，你跟許多人對著幹。」她要求襲擊者交出武器，兩人拒絕<ref name="tele">{{en}}{{Citation|last=Duffin|first=Claire|title=Mum talked down Woolwich terrorists who told her: 'We want to start a war in London tonight'|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=22 May 2013|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10074881/Mum-talked-down-Woolwich-terrorists-who-told-her-We-want-to-start-a-war-in-London-tonight.html|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523010507/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10074881/Mum-talked-down-Woolwich-terrorists-who-told-her-We-want-to-start-a-war-in-London-tonight.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

據報一名襲擊者跳過屍體，向巴士上的乘客要求拍照，另一名襲擊者在現場宣告他們發動襲擊的理由：

{{quote|「我們殺死這男人的唯一理由，是因為每一天都有穆斯林被英軍所殺，這英兵是其中一員，此乃[[以眼還眼|以眼還眼]]，以牙還牙。[[真主|真主]]在上，我們向全能真主起誓，我們不停戰鬥直至你離開我們。這樣我們才可以生活在[[伊斯蘭教法|伊斯蘭教法]]下的穆斯林土地。為什麼追趕我們和標籤我們做極端份子和殺害我們？很多人都是極端份子，你是其中一個。當你丟下炸彈，你以為只殺了目標一人卻將他一家人連根拔起。這就是現實。真主在上，如果我看到你的母親推著輪車，我會幫她上樓梯，這是我的天性。但我們只能跟從《[[可蘭經|可蘭經]]》〈[[懺悔_(可蘭經)|懺悔]]〉（《可蘭經》第九章），通過很多，很多經文，《可蘭經》各篇說我們一定決戰他們如他們決戰我們，以眼還眼，以牙還牙。很抱歉今日讓那女士看到這一幕，但在我們的地方，婦女每日都見到同樣場面，你們永不會安全。推翻你們的政府吧，他們不關心你。你覺得我們開槍之際會捉到[[大衛·卡梅倫|大衛·卡梅倫]]嗎？你覺得政治家會死嗎？不，死的是這平凡的傢伙，像你，和你的孩子。因此，攏脫他們吧，告訴他們把部隊撤回來，那麼我們……那麼你們都能生活在和平之中。離開我們的土地你們就能生活在和平之中。這就是我所說的。真主祝福穆罕默德以來的和平<ref name="Transcript">{{en}}{{cite web|first=Mark|last=Durie|url=http://markdurie.blogspot.com.au/2013/05/the-woolwich-killing-we-must-fight-them.html|title=The Woolwich Killing: "We must fight them as they fight us."|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2014-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717081842/http://www.markdurie.blogspot.com.au/2013/05/the-woolwich-killing-we-must-fight-them.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」}}

襲擊者待在原地，[[獲授權配備火槍人員|備槍警察]]於下午2:34分抵達，兩名襲擊者舉槍和刀指向警察，警察連開八槍，八槍全中襲擊者<ref name="guard3"/><ref>{{en}}{{Citation|publisher=BBC|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22653593|place=UK|title=Woolwich aftermath|date=24 May 2013|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2013-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610174111/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22653593|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現場檢獲槍、刀和菜刀，受害者證實死亡<ref name='BBC'/>。

===嫌犯===

嫌犯邁克爾·阿德博拉荷（{{lang-en|Michael Adebolajo}}），28歲、邁克爾·艾迪波瓦爾（{{lang-en|Michael Adebowale}}），22歲<ref name=GuardianWA>{{en}}The Guardian, ''[http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/23/woolwich-attack-suspect-michael-adebolajo Woolich attack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/23/woolwich-attack-suspect-michael-adebolajo |date=20130624190459 }}'', 23-05-3013, (retrieved 25 May 2013)</ref>，是尼日利亞裔英國穆斯林<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324659404578502790328797014.html|title=Second Suspect in London Attack Named|date=24 May 2013|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|author=Cassell Bryan-Low|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013094808/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324659404578502790328797014.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兩人任職[[保安|保安]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22634468|title=Woolwich attack: Suspects known to security services|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523170328/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22634468|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

邁克爾·阿德博拉荷生於[[蘭貝斯|蘭貝斯]]一個[[基督教|基督教]]家庭<ref name=Suspects>{{en}}{{cite news |url= http://news.sky.com/story/1094560/woolwich-terror-murder-suspect-named |title=Woolwich Terror Murder Suspect Named  |publisher=BSkyB |date=23 May 2013 |accessdate=23 May 2013}}</ref><ref name=Suspectsbbc>{{en}}{{cite news |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22636624 |title= Woolwich murder: who are the suspects? |publisher= BBC |date= 24 May 2013 |accessdate= 24 May 2013 |archive-date= 2013-05-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130523165833/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22636624 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，他在[[格林威治大學|格林威治大學]]研讀[[社會學|社會學]]。根據伊斯蘭教士[[安曾·喬杜里|安曾·喬杜里]]說，2003年英國當局取締伊斯蘭組織[[移民_(組織)|移民]]時，阿德博拉荷由基督教改信[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]<ref name=GuardianWA/><ref name="age">{{en}}{{cite news|author=Sengupta, Kim|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/man-and-woman-arrested-on-suspicion-of-conspiracy-to-murder-victim-of-woolwich-machete-attack-named-as-drummer-lee-rigby-8628583.html|title=Man and woman arrested on suspicion of conspiracy to murder victim of Woolwich machete attack, named as Drummer Lee Rigby|work=The Independent|date=23 May 2013|accessdate=23 May 2013|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130615055457/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/man-and-woman-arrested-on-suspicion-of-conspiracy-to-murder-victim-of-woolwich-machete-attack-named-as-drummer-lee-rigby-8628583.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿德博拉荷已經長時間在激進伊斯蘭組織活動<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10077439/Woolwich-attack-why-was-suspect-Michael-Adebolajo-free-to-kill.html|title=Woolwich attack: why was suspect Michael Adebolajo free to kill?|date=May 23, 2013|newspaper=The Telegraph|author=Tom Whitehead, David Barrett and Steven Swinford|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-date=2013-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524103151/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/terrorism-in-the-uk/10077439/Woolwich-attack-why-was-suspect-Michael-Adebolajo-free-to-kill.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿德博拉荷的朋友阿布·努撒巴在BBC新聞之夜訪談中表示，[[軍情五處|軍情五處]]曾經接觸過阿德博拉荷，阿德博拉荷不滿他們追問「某個人」的相關資訊，軍情五處問阿德博拉荷是否願意替他們工作，阿德博拉荷拒絕了他們<ref name=20130525urq>{{en}}Urquhart, Conal; Dodd, Vikram (25 May 2013). [http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/25/woolwich-suspect-kenya-torture "Woolwich suspect's friend arrested after appearing on Newsnight"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2013/may/25/woolwich-suspect-kenya-torture |date=20130616050929 }}. ''The Guardian''.</ref><ref name=BBC22664468 >{{en}}BBC, [http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22664468 Newsnight] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-22664468 |date=20130525013017 }}, 25 May 2013, (retrieved 25 May 2013)</ref>。阿布·努撒巴在BBC新聞之夜訪談後遭到逮捕<ref name=20130525urq/>。

